name: Music Video Submissions
overview:
MusicVideoSubmissions.com (MVS), subsidiary of Trendsetter Media and Marketing, is an online music video distribution company. The website is a DIY style interface created to provide music video placement on over 30 different television, online, and on-demand networks as well as retail outlets. While network airplay is not guaranteed, the service does guarantee that each video submitted will be sent in the proper specifications, viewed, considered, and given feedback. The company was designed specifically to meet the growing needs of independent artists and smaller label artists in a range of genres and budgets.

Additionally, MVS, offers other music video promotion services. Such services include social networking seeding, Vevo account set-up, video duplication, and closed captioning.
